result.name: Lady 13 Kitchen

reviews.text:
Stumbled across the shop one night and decided to give it a try.  Since then, I have came back a few times and brought a few friends over.

Choice of Chicken broth or beef broth noodles, or rice.  I like how the chicken soup base isn't too oily, but also strong flavor.  Choice of different types of noodles, I have tried a few by now and so far so good.  Noodles are served with a hot metal bowl, food will remain hot/warm while you eat.  Price isn't expensive and definitely recommend a try.

This place was packed but we only had to wait for 10 min! I got the noodles with the shredded chicken and chicken char siu for lunch...Which was delicious and was a much better deal than the regular price menu since it comes with a pop! The noodles came as a mix of the thicker and thinner vermicelli... which was something new! They have different floats with different names like black cow which basically means coke and vanilla ice cream but I didn't try! My friend had the noodles with beef brisket but she found it a bit dry and card! They also gave out complimentary shrimp crackers! The decor was interesting as everything was basically copper or brown :)

offering a different dining experience in Mongkok, it's more systematic in terms of nicer decor, well-designed menu, finer touch on setup.  but it's not delivery good value considering the price vs portion size.

Yell at customers. The restaurant is only half full when I arrived and I saw an empty table. As long as I walked towards the empty table, the restaurant owner yelled at me and insisted me to share the table with other customers. The moment she yelled, I can see that some of the customers are in shock, wondering what happened. She could have asked politely if I mind sharing the table. Instead, she yelled. If you can withstand her poor temper, please feel free to go.

Nice food and bad service.
We ordered 4 sets. They forgot 2 of our drinks. We brought that up right after paying. Staff A got annoyed immediately and asked us to wait. And then she asked us to approach staff B. Staff B brought us back to staff A. Staff A said we have to pay extra to take away the drinks and blamed us for not reminding her about the drinks. We gave up (I can have as much tea as I want back in office anyway. No point to argue in a 0-cs restaurant.)
Chicken rice was fatty but delicious. Chili paste matched with the chicken rice very well.
Not going back anytime soon.

result.name: 十三姨廚房

reviews.text: 又好食又親切❤️
湯底沒有味精👍 涼拌什菜👍

Stumbled across the shop one night and decided to give it a try.  Since then, I have came back a few times and brought a few friends over.

Choice of Chicken broth or beef broth noodles, or rice.  I like how the chicken soup base isn't too oily, but also strong flavor.  Choice of different types of noodles, I have tried a few by now and so far so good.  Noodles are served with a hot metal bowl, food will remain hot/warm while you eat.  Price isn't expensive and definitely recommend a try.
每次經過都好多人排隊，今晚算少人，點了十三么面和大三元飯，味道只是普通。但是！服務態度超好所以比足5星，成日睇下d客有咩須要，比豉油，睇下使唔使執碟，有新客到比張凳仔放袋，好耐冇去過咁細心用心的食肆

一個人入座，無茶無前菜。迫住叫杯甜到爆$20檸檬柚子蜜。 
埋單連加一服務費$125.
埋單問個收銀女仕，可能是老闆娘。
俾佢問返轉頭，無茶點解唔問佢。
又話補返杯茶。已經埋單企係門口。仲話打包俾我拎走。佩服!
個雞肉义燒，又淡又鞋
花鵰蕃茄幾特別，不過平蕃茄無乜味。浪費左個特式
總結。。不會再去
